# Bricks Order 

## OOD

```
BricksOrderTDD - TDD Unit Test Cases
|-- CreateOrderTest() : Verify the Order creation with valid quantity
|-- CreateOrderWithInvalidQtyTest()    : Verify the Order creation with invalid quantity
|-- getOrderTest() : Verify Get Order details with valid Order ref number input
|-- getOrderWithInvalidRefNoTest() : Verify Get Order details with invalid Order ref number input
|-- updateOrderTest() : Verify Update  Order with valid input
|-- updateOrderInvalidInputTest()    : Verify Update of Order with  invalid input
|-- fulFillOrderTest() : Verify Dispatch Order functionality with valid input
|-- fulFillOrderInvalidInputTest() : Verify Dispatch Order functionality with Invalid input
|-- updateOrderForDispatchedOrderTest() : Verify update order functionality for dispatched order
|-- getAllOrdersTest() :

BricksOrder - Model
|-- orderRefNo
|-- orderQty
|-- Status
|-- createdDate

BricksOrderController : Handles requests for the Order service.
|-- orderData : Map object used to data storage/retrieval
|-- createOrder(): Creates Order based on client request
|-- getOrder(): Get order details by passing order ref no 
|-- getAllOrders(): Get All created Orders
|-- updateOrder(): Updates Order qty and also Status by passing order ref no

BricksOrderClient : 
|-- main() : Main method to run the client application
|-- createOrder(): Creates Order which takes the new orders
|-- getOrder():  Get order details by passing order ref no 
|-- getAllOrders(): Get All created Orders
|-- updateOrder(): Updates Order qty and also Status by passing order ref no
|-- fulFilOrder : Fulfils the order by status dispatched by passing order ref no

TDD Unit Test Cases
File attaches with name of BricksOrder_TDD_TC




